Another example, to show off:<p>By running this code:<p><pre><code>    CloudDeploy[
      FormFunction[
        &quot;text&quot; -> &quot;String&quot;, 
        Classify[&quot;FacebookTopic&quot;, #text, &quot;TopProbabilities&quot;] &, 
        &quot;JSON&quot;
      ],
      Permissions -> &quot;Public&quot;
    ]
</code></pre>
I get a web form that can be used to enter arbitrary text and have social media topic inferred on it:<p><a href="https://www.wolframcloud.com/objects/0cda973b-8e12-43d7-a9d3-e32b94a58b74" rel="nofollow">https://www.wolframcloud.com/objects/0cda973b-8e12-43d7-a9d3...</a><p>Try something like &quot;I just had the most amazing meal at Four Burgers today&quot;.
